top_contracts.description: TASK ORDER (TO) 47QFCA21F0018 IS HEREBY AWARDED TO BOOZ ALLEN HAMILTON, INC. (BAH) TO PROVIDE ENTERPRISE LEVEL DATA TO THE OUSD(C), AND ITS STRATEGIC PARTNERS (I.E., DOD FOURTH ESTATE, DOD DEPARTMENTS, AND IC COMMUNITY).
TRANSFORMATION TWENTY-ONE TOTAL TECHNOLOGY NEXT GENERATION (T4NG) TASK ORDER - BENEFITS INTEGRATED DELIVERY

PRODUCT AND TECHNOLOGY ECOSYSTEM MANAGEMENT SERVICES (PTEMS)WHICH INCLUDES PRODUCT DELIVERY AND LIFECYCLE MANAGEMENT TO TRANSFORM VA BY TAPPING INTO EMERGING TECHNOLOGIES, CONNECTING DEVELOPERS WITH VA DATA, AND MAKING HUMAN CENTERED DESIGN (HCD).

THE PURPOSE OF THIS EFFORT IS TO ACQUIRE CONTRACTOR SERVICES TO PROVIDE REAL-TIME, COMPREHENSIVE THREAT ANALYSIS AND ASSESSMENT, TRAINING DEVELOPMENT AND DELIVERY, READINESS AND MODERNIZATION SUPPORT, AND LOGISTICS AND EQUIPMENT SERVICES.
NEW TO - EHRM PMO IO SUPPORT
IGF::OT::IGF  INFORMATION TECHNOLOGY OPERATIONS AND SERVICES TRANSFORMATION SUPPORT SERVICES
THE PURPOSE OF THIS MODIFICATION IS TO ACCEPT TRANSFER OF TASK ORDER (47QFCA18F0100) FROM FEDSIM TO GSA AAS REGION 8. THE NEW PIID IS 47QFRA20F0016.
IGF::OT::IGF  TRANSFORMATION TWENTY-ONE TOTAL TECHNOLOGY NEXT GENERATION (T4NG) TASK ORDER FOR ELECTRONIC HEALTH RECORD MODERNIZATION PROGRAM MANAGEMENT OFFICE SUPPORT.

THIS REPRESENTS AN ADMINISTRATIVE CONTINUANCE OF GSA FEDSIM TASK ORDER 47QFCA20F0009.  THIS EFFORT WILL BE ADMINISTERED BY GSA FAS REGION 1 UNDER TO NUMBER 47QFNA21F0001 BEGINNING ON THE EFFECTIVE AWARD DATE OF 1 NOVEMBER 2020.
THE CONTRACTOR SHALL PROVIDE SHIPPABLE PRODUCTS, OPERATIONS SUPPORT, AND SECURITY COMPLIANCE FOR THE HEALTH SERVICES PORTFOLIO.
CDM DEFEND GROUP BD  BRIDGE TASK ORDER
THE JAIC REQUIRES OPEN ARCHITECTURE TECHNICAL SERVICES AND PRODUCTS (SOFTWARE AND/OR HARDWARE) ACROSS THE FULL SPECTRUM OF AI-ENABLED CAPABILITIES TO SUPPORT THE JWNMI.

limitations: USAspending amounts from spending_by_award are award totals as returned by the endpoint and may not equal obligations within FY2024.
FEC individual contributions are filtered by exact employer string and will omit other Booz Allen variants (e.g., BOOZ-ALLEN, BOOZ ALLEN HAMILTON INC.).
Cross-links between contributions and agencies are contextual and based on committee oversight relevance; they do not demonstrate causality or improper influence.
